{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"146548-mesin-nenek-yang-menarik","title":"Mesin Nenek yang Menarik","description":"Sooraj dan neneknya SUKA mencipta! Sertailah mereka dalam pengembaraan terbaru: dengan menggunakan mesin untuk membuat barfi kelapa!","language":"Malay","langCode":"ms","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Lydia Aderus"],"illustrators":["Rajiv Eipe"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/146548-mesin-nenek-yang-menarik"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/712718/size3/9afb2c00f7a211ff4c8699e66ca7db0b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/712718/size6/9afb2c00f7a211ff4c8699e66ca7db0b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30169/size6/d207276a2815a071558385c615a4b8cb.jpg","text":"“Nenek! Nenek! Bolehkah kita membuat barfi kelapa hari ini?” Sooraj bertanya kepada neneknya.\n“BOLEEEEEEEH TAAAAAAK?”","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30284/size6/1f1845b3937db71d57097700da2554b1.jpg","text":"“Hee hee hee! Hanya jika anda membantu saya membuatnya, eh?” jawab Nenek.\n“YAY!”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30056/size6/a01635d8b9b4cd72c320d8fb5aa29cc2.jpg","text":"“Siap?” teriak Sooraj.\n“Siap!” kata Nenek.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30731/size6/5d387c832dfc2d8d6e086bf82f9e6269.jpg","text":"“Kami hanya akan memilih \n       \n         \n   kelapa yang sudah masak, okay?\n     \n         \n  Yang berwarna coklat...\n       \n         \n Hati-hati! Semuanya turun!”\n   \n         \n    WHOOOSH... WHUMP!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30060/size6/6c476755eef54f036cedb0b6fd497f0f.jpg","text":"“Sekarang untuk          \nmembuang kulitnya...”   \nPotch! CRAANKK!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30279/size6/484adb7c7ebb9ebb4fdf2092c25e926f.jpg","text":"Perut Sooraj pun berbunyi: “GRRRRRR!”\nNenek ketawa.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30062/size6/533efd06df4be288862d4e89ff04bc26.jpg","text":"“Kemudian kami peCAHKAN\ncengkerang... seperti INI!”\nKHATAK!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30732/size6/9e13646576c48649aecb5aa3c3efab5e.jpg","text":"“Dan paaaaaarrrruuut buaaaaaahnyaaaaa!”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30152/size6/28802bc5377967007a502c69b077a3e1.jpg","text":"“Masukkan ke dalam kuali dengan semua bahan yang lain...”\n“Baunya SANGAT sedap, Nenek!”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30734/size6/b95cb78abce35280c1ca70735be5d798.jpg","text":"“Kemudian kami tuangkan semuanya ke atas dulang... Tunggu ia sejuk, baba!”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30737/size6/8119a7fcefcdbcbcb85e1895c12541ca.jpg","text":"“Sekarang potong                         \nhirisan yang kemas...”                        \nSQUEAK\nSQUEAK","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30287/size6/c2ace437c2e968656969c7158d3b4ecf.jpg","text":"“YIPPEE! Barfi kelapa kami sudah siap untuk dimakan!”\n                                             “YUM YUM YUM!”","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30157/size6/69dd429e6d3e945223839ec85adf3f34.jpg","text":"Barfi Nenek dibuat menggunakan MESIN YANG SEDERHANA! Mesin memudahkan kerja. Terdapat enam jenis mesin:\n1. Satah condong\n2. Tuil\n3. Roda dan gandar","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/30159/size6/862c132774e3089a686ee8f1eb517986.jpg","text":"4. Baji\n5. Takal\n6. Skru\nBolehkah anda mengenalpasti mesin yang digunakan oleh Sooraj dan Nenek dalam proses pembuatan barfi kelapa?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":14,"words":160}}